00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:59,179
[SPEAKER_00] gledalo duše nekako,

686
00:34:59,179 --> 00:35:01,360
[SPEAKER_00] baš nekako pomaže ljudima,

687
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:05,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji možda nisu sami sposobni izrasti sve što im se događa u duši,

688
00:35:05,340 --> 00:35:08,019
[SPEAKER_00] onda se oni pronalaze u takvim tekstojima.

689
00:35:08,019 --> 00:35:08,579
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

690
00:35:08,579 --> 00:35:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, jedna od,

691
00:35:10,539 --> 00:35:12,079
[SPEAKER_01] definitiv jedna od stvari je,

692
00:35:12,079 --> 00:35:14,300
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću biti iskren,

693
00:35:14,460 --> 00:35:17,519
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam se dugo mučio to javno objavljivati.

694
00:35:17,519 --> 00:35:20,559
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo, ja sam dio jedne zajednice

695
00:35:20,559 --> 00:35:22,920
[SPEAKER_01] i mi fratri, naravno,

696
00:35:22,920 --> 00:35:24,539
[SPEAKER_01] kao i svaki drugi ljudi,

697
00:35:24,539 --> 00:35:25,300
[SPEAKER_01] nekad znamo,

698
00:35:25,300 --> 00:35:26,719
[SPEAKER_01] možda biti malo,

699
00:35:26,719 --> 00:35:27,739
[SPEAKER_01] da tako se izrazim,

700
00:35:27,739 --> 00:35:28,699
[SPEAKER_01] možda grubo,

701
00:35:28,699 --> 00:35:31,159
[SPEAKER_01] nemilosrdni jedni prema drugima

702
00:35:31,159 --> 00:35:32,920
[SPEAKER_01] i nekako ismijati,

703
00:35:32,920 --> 00:35:34,400
[SPEAKER_01] ismijati, ne znam,

704
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:35,420
[SPEAKER_01] neku umjetnost,

705
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] način pisanja, izriča i tako dalje,

706
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] što je sastavni dio života,

707
00:35:39,539 --> 00:35:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] neke stvari u životu ne možemo izbiti.

708
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:43,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mislim da je to nužno sad nešto loše,

709
00:35:43,139 --> 00:35:44,219
[SPEAKER_01] ali je tako.

710
00:35:44,900 --> 00:35:47,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se dugo mučio

711
00:35:47,300 --> 00:35:48,699
[SPEAKER_01] izaći u javni prostor,

712
00:35:48,699 --> 00:35:51,739
[SPEAKER_01] zbog svojih osobnih nekih obzira,

713
00:35:51,739 --> 00:35:52,980
[SPEAKER_01] kojih je bilo jako puno,

714
00:35:52,980 --> 00:35:56,260
[SPEAKER_01] strahova i tog nekog osjećaja,

715
00:35:56,260 --> 00:35:58,400
[SPEAKER_01] šta ako me neko sastruže,

716
00:35:58,400 --> 00:35:59,840
[SPEAKER_01] šta ako neko uzme to

717
00:35:59,840 --> 00:36:02,420
[SPEAKER_01] i napadnete su šta ti pišeš,

718
00:36:02,420 --> 00:36:03,179
[SPEAKER_01] šta ti iznosiš,

719
00:36:03,179 --> 00:36:04,940
[SPEAKER_01] šta ti kao nešto osjećaš,

720
00:36:04,940 --> 00:36:05,860
[SPEAKER_01] tebi nešto, ne znam,

721
00:36:05,860 --> 00:36:07,400
[SPEAKER_01] Bog govori ili,

722
00:36:07,400 --> 00:36:08,500
[SPEAKER_01] kako bih rekao,

723
00:36:08,500 --> 00:36:09,840
[SPEAKER_01] ili nešto treće.

724
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:11,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se puno mučio,

725
00:36:11,599 --> 00:36:14,719
[SPEAKER_01] ima jedna riječ koja isto meni je jako draga

726
00:36:14,719 --> 00:36:16,300
[SPEAKER_01] i ona se isto provlači dosta kroz kinzu,

727
00:36:16,300 --> 00:36:17,179
[SPEAKER_01] to je ranjivost.

728
00:36:17,179 --> 00:36:19,179
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo stvarno ranjivi

729
00:36:19,179 --> 00:36:23,800
[SPEAKER_01] i nekada tu ranjivost ne možemo pobjeći od nje.

730
00:36:24,400 --> 00:36:27,119
[SPEAKER_01] I meni je trebalo puno vremena

731
00:36:27,119 --> 00:36:29,980
[SPEAKER_01] da uđem u taj neki,

732
00:36:29,980 --> 00:36:30,639
[SPEAKER_01] ja imam reći tako,

733
00:36:30,639 --> 00:36:31,519
[SPEAKER_01] u obzor slobode,

734
00:36:31,519 --> 00:36:33,260
[SPEAKER_01] u neko ozrače slobode,

735
00:36:33,260 --> 00:36:36,019
[SPEAKER_01] ne da me nije briga šta neko govori,

736
00:36:36,019 --> 00:36:38,019
[SPEAKER_01] jer uvijek će ljudi govoriti,

737
00:36:38,019 --> 00:36:38,739
[SPEAKER_01] komentirati,

738
00:36:38,739 --> 00:36:39,320
[SPEAKER_01] tumačiti,

739
00:36:39,320 --> 00:36:40,639
[SPEAKER_01] to ne možemo izbjeći,

740
00:36:40,639 --> 00:36:44,380
[SPEAKER_01] ali da ja slobodno mogu stajati za svojih riječi.

741
00:36:44,380 --> 00:36:48,119
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, da se ja ne plašim onoga što sam ja napisao

742
00:36:48,119 --> 00:36:50,920
[SPEAKER_01] i ako bi me sutra neko rekao šta je ovo,

743
00:36:50,920 --> 00:36:52,659
[SPEAKER_01] da ja mogu reći šta je to.

744
00:36:53,119 --> 00:36:54,639
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to mi je baš,

745
00:36:54,639 --> 00:36:56,980
[SPEAKER_01] baš mi je trebalo dugo razdoblje,

746
00:36:56,980 --> 00:36:58,880
[SPEAKER_01] da to nekako se prelomi u meni,

747
00:36:58,880 --> 00:37:00,159
[SPEAKER_01] da to izađe van.

748
00:37:00,159 --> 00:37:01,320
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, danas,

749
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:02,960
[SPEAKER_01] kako bih rekao,

750
00:37:02,960 --> 00:37:05,679
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi možda neki koji imaju dara,

751
00:37:05,679 --> 00:37:06,780
[SPEAKER_01] talenta za pisanje,

752
00:37:06,780 --> 00:37:07,940
[SPEAKER_01] možda zaziru od toga,

753
00:37:07,940 --> 00:37:10,300
[SPEAKER_01] baš zbog tih obzira,

754
00:37:10,300 --> 00:37:12,039
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, strahova i tako dalje,

755
00:37:12,039 --> 00:37:13,300
[SPEAKER_01] tuđih očiju,

756
00:37:13,300 --> 00:37:14,860
[SPEAKER_01] koje nekad isto tako znaju biti,

757
00:37:14,860 --> 00:37:15,579
[SPEAKER_01] ali nemalo sr,

758
00:37:15,579 --> 00:37:18,300
[SPEAKER_01] nekad nešto pogledaju, pročitaju i tako dalje.

759
00:37:18,300 --> 00:37:21,639
[SPEAKER_01] A kako bih rekao,

760
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:23,159
[SPEAKER_01] a negdje drugdje ono,

761
00:37:23,159 --> 00:37:25,960
[SPEAKER_01] taj strah od tog mogućeg,

762
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:27,360
[SPEAKER_01] jel, komentara,

763
00:37:27,360 --> 00:37:29,659
[SPEAKER_01] koji nečalost nekad je,

764
00:37:29,659 --> 00:37:31,539
[SPEAKER_01] je osobitno na tim društvenim mrežama,

765
00:37:31,539 --> 00:37:33,420
[SPEAKER_01] kad imate ljude koji vam komentiraju,

766
00:37:33,420 --> 00:37:34,900
[SPEAKER_01] nema nime ni prezimena,

767
00:37:34,900 --> 00:37:36,539
[SPEAKER_01] jako ružno,

768
00:37:36,539 --> 00:37:38,519
[SPEAKER_01] i nekad mi se više poistovjetimo

769
00:37:38,519 --> 00:37:40,260
[SPEAKER_01] s tim jednim negativnim komentarom,

770
00:37:40,260 --> 00:37:41,840
[SPEAKER_01] nego možda tisuću drugih,

771
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:43,320
[SPEAKER_01] koji su vrlo pozitivni,

772
00:37:43,380 --> 00:37:45,199
[SPEAKER_01] hrabrujući i poticajni i tako dalje.

773
00:37:45,199 --> 00:37:46,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ali,

774
00:37:46,199 --> 00:37:47,260
[SPEAKER_01] meni je taj moment,

775
00:37:47,260 --> 00:37:48,340
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam ih shvatio,

776
00:37:48,340 --> 00:37:48,840
[SPEAKER_01] jel,

777
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:51,239
[SPEAKER_01] da je to nešto baš moje,

778
00:37:51,239 --> 00:37:52,079
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

779
00:37:52,079 --> 00:37:54,659
[SPEAKER_01] što je gospodin meni darovao,

780
00:37:54,659 --> 00:37:57,300
[SPEAKER_01] što je dio mog tog iskustva,

781
00:37:57,300 --> 00:37:57,599
[SPEAKER_01] jel,

782
00:37:57,599 --> 00:38:01,019
[SPEAKER_01] i da ja to sad nemam problema podijeliti s drugima,

783
00:38:01,019 --> 00:38:01,760
[SPEAKER_01] da sam nemam,

784
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:03,199
[SPEAKER_01] nemam sad više problema,

785
00:38:03,199 --> 00:38:05,340
[SPEAKER_01] da sva čije oči gledaju to,

786
00:38:05,340 --> 00:38:07,380
[SPEAKER_01] i oči koje će se možda natopiti suzama,

787
00:38:07,380 --> 00:38:09,599
[SPEAKER_01] jer će naći neku lijekovitu misl,

788
00:38:09,599 --> 00:38:10,739
[SPEAKER_01] lijekovitu riječ za sebe,

789
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] doni koji će, ono,

790
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,280
[SPEAKER_01] možda zaklopiti kingu i reći,

791
00:38:13,280 --> 00:38:14,539
[SPEAKER_01] ono, šta on, šta mali,

792
00:38:14,539 --> 00:38:14,760
[SPEAKER_01] jel.

793
00:38:14,760 --> 00:38:15,860
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da,

794
00:38:15,860 --> 00:38:18,159
[SPEAKER_01] i ovaj moment mi osobe,

795
00:38:18,159 --> 00:38:19,039
[SPEAKER_01] bi to bio drag,

796
00:38:19,039 --> 00:38:21,179
[SPEAKER_01] što su se meni javljali ljude,

797
00:38:21,179 --> 00:38:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo sad isto vidim,

798
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] na osobi to zadnjih možda tijan dana,

799
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:25,280
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

800
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:25,739
[SPEAKER_01] napiše,

801
00:38:25,739 --> 00:38:27,579
[SPEAKER_01] napiše ti osoba koja te nikad nije vidjela,

802
00:38:27,579 --> 00:38:27,900
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

803
00:38:27,900 --> 00:38:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] iz Njemačke, Austrije,

804
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:32,059
[SPEAKER_01] nekog drugog mjesta iz Hrvatske,

805
00:38:32,059 --> 00:38:32,780
[SPEAKER_01] kaže,

806
00:38:32,780 --> 00:38:34,019
[SPEAKER_01] dušu sam isplakala.

807
00:38:34,019 --> 00:38:34,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, mislim,

808
00:38:34,679 --> 00:38:36,460
[SPEAKER_01] samo ti se javi,

809
00:38:36,460 --> 00:38:36,960
[SPEAKER_01] napiše,

810
00:38:36,960 --> 00:38:39,639
[SPEAKER_01] nikad te neko nije vidio,

811
00:38:39,639 --> 00:38:41,260
[SPEAKER_01] ali tu se pronađe,

812
00:38:41,260 --> 00:38:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] i tu pronađe neki dubliji smisao.

813
00:38:43,539 --> 00:38:44,179
[SPEAKER_01] I to je meni,

814
00:38:44,179 --> 00:38:45,940
[SPEAKER_01] to je meni nekako i teološki,

815
00:38:45,940 --> 00:38:46,380
[SPEAKER_01] jer, ono,

816
00:38:46,380 --> 00:38:48,679
[SPEAKER_01] mi baš imamo to i u Svetom pismu,

817
00:38:48,679 --> 00:38:50,159
[SPEAKER_01] i ušlo je u liturgiju crkve,

818
00:38:50,159 --> 00:38:51,940
[SPEAKER_01] njegove nas modrice izliječiše.

819
00:38:51,940 --> 00:38:53,139
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

820
00:38:53,139 --> 00:38:55,699
[SPEAKER_01] nas je gospodinova rana izliječila,

821
00:38:55,699 --> 00:38:56,480
[SPEAKER_01] i ozdravila,

822
00:38:56,480 --> 00:38:59,139
[SPEAKER_01] i te naše rane,

823
00:38:59,139 --> 00:39:00,179
[SPEAKER_01] koje su nekako,

824
00:39:00,179 --> 00:39:02,119
[SPEAKER_01] kad su stopljene s gospodinovim,

825
00:39:02,119 --> 00:39:04,599
[SPEAKER_01] kako je to ljekovito za ljudske duše.

826
00:39:04,719 --> 00:39:05,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ja moram priznati da je meni,

827
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:06,940
[SPEAKER_01] za me najbolji komentar,

828
00:39:06,940 --> 00:39:08,900
[SPEAKER_01] lijepo je čuti komentar svakati,

829
00:39:08,900 --> 00:39:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] čast, ovo vam je,

830
00:39:09,960 --> 00:39:11,239
[SPEAKER_01] super, ovo vam se super sviđa,

831
00:39:11,239 --> 00:39:12,159
[SPEAKER_01] jao, kako ovo, dobro,

832
00:39:12,159 --> 00:39:13,139
[SPEAKER_01] sve je to lijepo.

833
00:39:13,139 --> 00:39:14,739
[SPEAKER_01] Najbolji komentar,

834
00:39:14,739 --> 00:39:17,239
[SPEAKER_01] je kad osoba reagira.

835
00:39:17,239 --> 00:39:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] Kad osoba napiše nešto osobno,

836
00:39:20,079 --> 00:39:21,800
[SPEAKER_01] kako su na nju utjecali te riječi,

837
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:24,039
[SPEAKER_01] šta te riječi njoj znači.

838
00:39:24,039 --> 00:39:24,539
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ja,

839
00:39:24,539 --> 00:39:26,099
[SPEAKER_01] ja tada zastanem,

840
00:39:26,099 --> 00:39:26,380
[SPEAKER_01] predstavljam,

841
00:39:26,380 --> 00:39:27,099
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne mogu vjerovat,

842
00:39:27,099 --> 00:39:28,760
[SPEAKER_01] da to ima toliki domet.

843
00:39:28,760 --> 00:39:30,159
[SPEAKER_01] Jer za mene je to bilo,

844
00:39:30,780 --> 00:39:32,019
[SPEAKER_01] gospodin i ja i Hrvanje,

845
00:39:32,019 --> 00:39:32,920
[SPEAKER_01] nema tu svjedoka,

846
00:39:32,920 --> 00:39:35,159
[SPEAKER_01] imam tu negdje na par mjesta,

847
00:39:35,159 --> 00:39:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] ono, zaštićeni od nepozvanih svjedoka.

848
00:39:38,500 --> 00:39:39,519
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, jednostavno,

849
00:39:39,519 --> 00:39:40,900
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam bio zaštićen na neki način,

850
00:39:40,900 --> 00:39:41,880
[SPEAKER_01] od nepozvanih svjedoka,

851
00:39:41,880 --> 00:39:43,880
[SPEAKER_01] jer to je nekoj mojoj unutarnjnoj borbi.

852
00:39:43,880 --> 00:39:47,059
[SPEAKER_01] I sad kad vidim koliko to,

853
00:39:47,059 --> 00:39:47,639
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

854
00:39:47,639 --> 00:39:49,760
[SPEAKER_01] kako to utječe na druge ljude,

855
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:51,019
[SPEAKER_01] ja moram priznati,

856
00:39:51,019 --> 00:39:52,460
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam nekad stvarno ovaj,

857
00:39:52,460 --> 00:39:53,900
[SPEAKER_01] baš se ono,

858
00:39:53,900 --> 00:39:56,300
[SPEAKER_01] učinio bih sebe malenim,

859
00:39:56,300 --> 00:39:56,619
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

860
00:39:56,619 --> 00:39:59,340
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu vjerovati da to ima toliki efekt

861
00:39:59,340 --> 00:40:00,559
[SPEAKER_01] i učinak,

862
00:40:00,559 --> 00:40:02,659
[SPEAKER_01] ali mi je jako drago,

863
00:40:02,659 --> 00:40:03,519
[SPEAKER_01] drago mi je,

864
00:40:03,519 --> 00:40:03,780
[SPEAKER_01] zato,

865
00:40:03,780 --> 00:40:05,619
[SPEAKER_01] ne stvarno,

866
00:40:05,619 --> 00:40:05,820
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

867
00:40:05,820 --> 00:40:06,139
[SPEAKER_01] drago mi je,

868
00:40:06,139 --> 00:40:06,699
[SPEAKER_01] naravno zbog mene,

869
00:40:06,699 --> 00:40:08,639
[SPEAKER_01] ali baš mi je ono drago,

870
00:40:08,639 --> 00:40:10,699
[SPEAKER_01] jer to ja znam da je gospodin dotaknuo dušu.

871
00:40:10,699 --> 00:40:12,380
[SPEAKER_01] Da nije to moje.

872
00:40:12,380 --> 00:40:14,059
[SPEAKER_01] Nemam ja tu snagu,

873
00:40:14,059 --> 00:40:14,699
[SPEAKER_01] tu moć,

874
00:40:14,699 --> 00:40:15,699
[SPEAKER_01] nisam ja tako,

875
00:40:15,699 --> 00:40:17,019
[SPEAKER_01] kako je rekao,

876
00:40:17,019 --> 00:40:18,280
[SPEAKER_01] svesilam da to mogu.

877
00:40:18,599 --> 00:40:20,619
[SPEAKER_01] To je baš gospodin dotaknuo dušu.

878
00:40:20,619 --> 00:40:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to mi je posebno

879
00:40:22,000 --> 00:40:24,019
[SPEAKER_01] i ovo što si kazao,

880
00:40:24,019 --> 00:40:25,079
[SPEAKER_01] jer li oni mogu,

881
00:40:25,079 --> 00:40:26,219
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi sebe pronađu

882
00:40:26,219 --> 00:40:27,639
[SPEAKER_01] i čitajući koliko tolije,

883
00:40:27,639 --> 00:40:28,460
[SPEAKER_01] koliko to na njih djeluje,

884
00:40:28,460 --> 00:40:30,039
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam stvarno nekad,

885
00:40:30,039 --> 00:40:31,139
[SPEAKER_01] ono, baš impresioniran.

886
00:40:31,139 --> 00:40:33,280
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, gospodin djelije preko vas.

887
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

888
00:40:33,599 --> 00:40:35,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kod su vam bili suradnici

889
00:40:35,900 --> 00:40:36,920
