01:11:46,180 --> 01:11:47,319
[SPEAKER_01] tri, četiri mjeseca,

2133
01:11:47,319 --> 01:11:48,659
[SPEAKER_01] da su mlađi svećenici,

2134
01:11:48,659 --> 01:11:49,439
[SPEAKER_01] uvjetno rečeno,

2135
01:11:49,920 --> 01:11:50,960
[SPEAKER_01] više tradicionalni,

2136
01:11:50,960 --> 01:11:53,680
[SPEAKER_01] vidiš ti ovo ne pije više vode,

2137
01:11:53,680 --> 01:11:55,060
[SPEAKER_01] ali mi to imamo,

2138
01:11:55,060 --> 01:11:55,560
[SPEAKER_01] mi to,

2139
01:11:55,560 --> 01:11:55,899
[SPEAKER_01] znaš,

2140
01:11:55,899 --> 01:11:57,079
[SPEAKER_01] u nas se misla slavi,

2141
01:11:57,079 --> 01:11:58,359
[SPEAKER_01] ja evo osobno,

2142
01:11:58,359 --> 01:11:59,319
[SPEAKER_01] ja se ne mogu sjetiti,

2143
01:11:59,319 --> 01:12:00,279
[SPEAKER_01] odrastao sam tu,

2144
01:12:00,279 --> 01:12:01,880
[SPEAKER_01] da sam ikad bio na nekoj,

2145
01:12:01,880 --> 01:12:03,279
[SPEAKER_01] am tako riješ nevaljanoj misi,

2146
01:12:03,279 --> 01:12:03,979
[SPEAKER_01] ili misi koja,

2147
01:12:03,979 --> 01:12:06,460
[SPEAKER_01] koja je bila puna nekakvih gluposti,

2148
01:12:06,579 --> 01:12:08,939
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo jednostavno navikli da to je to,

2149
01:12:08,939 --> 01:12:09,340
[SPEAKER_01] jeli,

2150
01:12:09,340 --> 01:12:09,880
[SPEAKER_01] to je to,

2151
01:12:09,880 --> 01:12:10,140
[SPEAKER_01] jeli,

2152
01:12:10,140 --> 01:12:11,739
[SPEAKER_01] i ovaj,

2153
01:12:11,739 --> 01:12:12,939
[SPEAKER_01] kako bih rekao,

2154
01:12:12,939 --> 01:12:14,060
[SPEAKER_01] ima te obnove,

2155
01:12:14,060 --> 01:12:15,260
[SPEAKER_01] Kanada opet,

2156
01:12:15,260 --> 01:12:16,760
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam prekratko u Kanadi,

2157
01:12:16,760 --> 01:12:18,079
[SPEAKER_01] za neki širi dojam,

2158
01:12:18,079 --> 01:12:19,479
[SPEAKER_01] još samo sam u jednom gradu,

2159
01:12:19,479 --> 01:12:21,920
[SPEAKER_01] nisam propovjedao na više nekih mjesta,

2160
01:12:21,920 --> 01:12:23,819
[SPEAKER_01] pa ne mogu baš suditi,

2161
01:12:23,819 --> 01:12:25,600
[SPEAKER_01] tamo,

2162
01:12:25,600 --> 01:12:30,260
[SPEAKER_01] to je da postoji neki osobit antikatolički stav,

2163
01:12:30,260 --> 01:12:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] u određenim krugovima,

2164
01:12:32,000 --> 01:12:36,340
[SPEAKER_01] da čini mi se samo malo više od 20,

2165
01:12:36,579 --> 01:12:40,819
[SPEAKER_01] posto uopće da je prisutnost katolika,

2166
01:12:40,819 --> 01:12:41,439
[SPEAKER_01] na misi,

2167
01:12:41,439 --> 01:12:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo je to nešto tanko,

2168
01:12:43,380 --> 01:12:43,739
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

2169
01:12:43,739 --> 01:12:46,300
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam točno statistiku,

2170
01:12:46,300 --> 01:12:46,939
[SPEAKER_01] ne bih želio,

2171
01:12:46,939 --> 01:12:48,060
[SPEAKER_01] kako bih rekao,

2172
01:12:48,060 --> 01:12:51,800
[SPEAKER_01] suflirati našim gledateljima nešto krivo,

2173
01:12:51,800 --> 01:12:55,460
[SPEAKER_01] jer stvarno prekratko sam tu za neki širi dojam,

2174
01:12:55,460 --> 01:12:56,380
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo,

2175
01:12:56,380 --> 01:12:56,699
[SPEAKER_01] primjer,

2176
01:12:56,699 --> 01:12:57,779
[SPEAKER_01] iz moje perspektive,

2177
01:12:57,779 --> 01:13:00,119
[SPEAKER_01] isto naši Hrvati,

2178
01:13:00,119 --> 01:13:01,800
[SPEAKER_01] kad su god nekakve prigode druge,

2179
01:13:01,800 --> 01:13:04,239
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je nekaka poseban događaj,

2180
01:13:04,239 --> 01:13:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] ili ima, ne znam, ručak,

2181
01:13:06,020 --> 01:13:06,640
[SPEAKER_01] ili neka večera,

2182
01:13:06,640 --> 01:13:07,279
[SPEAKER_01] nešto tako,

2183
01:13:07,279 --> 01:13:08,819
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek će biti više ljudi.

2184
01:13:08,819 --> 01:13:09,880
[SPEAKER_01] Regularno,

2185
01:13:09,880 --> 01:13:11,119
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek će to biti puno,

2186
01:13:11,119 --> 01:13:12,079
[SPEAKER_01] puno manji broj,

2187
01:13:12,079 --> 01:13:13,880
[SPEAKER_01] nego na takvim skupovima.

2188
01:13:13,880 --> 01:13:16,260
[SPEAKER_01] Što je naša neka realnost tamo?

2189
01:13:16,260 --> 01:13:18,640
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, kada smo se već malo dotakli

2190
01:13:18,640 --> 01:13:20,239
[SPEAKER_00] te teme evangelizacije,

2191
01:13:20,239 --> 01:13:22,020
[SPEAKER_00] kako crkva je danas nastupa?

2192
01:13:22,020 --> 01:13:24,520
[SPEAKER_00] Je li se crkva dovoljno ključila

2193
01:13:24,520 --> 01:13:28,140
[SPEAKER_00] u ovaj neki suvremeni vid evangelizacije?

2194
01:13:28,140 --> 01:13:30,239
[SPEAKER_00] Usjećam se iz podcasta

2195
01:13:30,239 --> 01:13:31,479
[SPEAKER_00] s fra Josipom,

2196
01:13:31,479 --> 01:13:34,100
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je on upravo taj internet

2197
01:13:34,100 --> 01:13:35,779
[SPEAKER_00] okarakterizirao

2198
01:13:35,779 --> 01:13:37,659
[SPEAKER_00] i što je njemu bio potica

2199
01:13:37,659 --> 01:13:38,720
[SPEAKER_00] za je duhovne vježbe,

2200
01:13:38,720 --> 01:13:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] da je to novi kontinent

2201
01:13:40,039 --> 01:13:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] na koji ti moraš doći evangelizirati.

2202
01:13:43,699 --> 01:13:45,279
[SPEAKER_01] Ja osobno mislim

2203
01:13:45,279 --> 01:13:47,800
[SPEAKER_01] da crkva još uvijek ima prostora,

2204
01:13:47,800 --> 01:13:50,319
[SPEAKER_01] ali ako ja uzmem neko razdoblje

2205
01:13:50,319 --> 01:13:52,460
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam ja došao u Fratre

2206
01:13:52,460 --> 01:13:53,239
[SPEAKER_01] do dan danas,

2207
01:13:53,239 --> 01:13:55,619
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim da je to enormni napredak.

2208
01:13:55,619 --> 01:13:58,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ima toga sve više,

2209
01:13:58,579 --> 01:14:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] sve to i kvalitetnije.

2210
01:14:01,000 --> 01:14:02,439
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno,

2211
01:14:02,439 --> 01:14:04,760
[SPEAKER_01] nekada, kako bih rekao,

2212
01:14:04,760 --> 01:14:06,520
[SPEAKER_01] neki su u istinu baš kvalitetni,

2213
01:14:06,520 --> 01:14:08,460
[SPEAKER_01] neki ciljano idu na određenu

2214
01:14:08,460 --> 01:14:09,439
[SPEAKER_01] dobnu skupinu,

2215
