2221
01:14:20,899 --> 01:14:23,020
[SPEAKER_01] Netko puno bolje radi s mladima,

2222
01:14:23,020 --> 01:14:25,399
[SPEAKER_01] neko je bolji realno u administraciji,

2223
01:14:25,399 --> 01:14:27,560
[SPEAKER_01] neko je bolji u nekakvom

2224
01:14:27,560 --> 01:14:28,479
