[SPEAKER_01] možda prisutnosti više lajka?

2227
01:14:31,079 --> 01:14:33,479
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja mislim da,

2228
01:14:33,479 --> 01:14:34,880
[SPEAKER_01] kako bih rekao,

2229
01:14:34,880 --> 01:14:37,720
[SPEAKER_01] da vaše djelovanje je ovaj,

2230
01:14:37,720 --> 01:14:39,039
[SPEAKER_01] kako bih rekao,

2231
