2234
01:14:42,619 --> 01:14:43,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ne govori nemo,

2235
01:14:43,300 --> 01:14:45,180
[SPEAKER_00] možda konkretne suradnje

2236
01:14:45,180 --> 01:14:46,680
[SPEAKER_00] između svećenika.

2237
01:14:46,680 --> 01:14:47,439
[SPEAKER_01] Absolutno.

2238
01:14:47,439 --> 01:14:47,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

2239
01:14:47,960 --> 01:14:49,779
[SPEAKER_01] ja osobno,

2240
01:14:49,779 --> 01:14:51,119
[SPEAKER_01] kako bih rekao,

2241
01:14:51,119 --> 01:14:52,579
[SPEAKER_01] baš pozitivno gledam

2242
01:14:52,579 --> 01:14:53,220
[SPEAKER_01] na veću,

2243
01:14:53,220 --> 01:14:54,779
[SPEAKER_01] veću uključenost lajka.

2244
01:14:54,779 --> 01:14:56,060
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno,

2245
01:14:56,060 --> 01:14:58,800
[SPEAKER_01] da se zadrži to neko temeljno

2246
01:14:58,800 --> 01:14:59,760
[SPEAKER_01] poštovanje

2247
01:14:59,760 --> 01:15:01,500
[SPEAKER_01] ministerijalnog svećenika

2248
01:15:01,500 --> 01:15:03,399
[SPEAKER_01] svećenika i tako dalje,

2249
01:15:03,399 --> 01:15:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer,

2250
01:15:04,000 --> 01:15:04,220
[SPEAKER_01] evo,

2251
01:15:04,220 --> 01:15:04,680
[SPEAKER_01] primjer se,

2252
01:15:04,680 --> 01:15:06,279
[SPEAKER_01] baš kontekst u kojem sam ja,

2253
01:15:06,279 --> 01:15:07,239
[SPEAKER_01] Amerike i Kanade,

2254
01:15:07,239 --> 01:15:10,260
[SPEAKER_01] je odveo totalno drugu stranu.

2255
01:15:10,260 --> 01:15:12,600
[SPEAKER_01] Lajci sve više počneš biti prisutan,

2256
01:15:12,600 --> 01:15:14,840
[SPEAKER_01] međutim onda dođe ti da lajk vodi župu,

2257
01:15:14,840 --> 01:15:17,060
[SPEAKER_01] svećenik je totalno marginaliziran.

2258
01:15:17,060 --> 01:15:18,479
[SPEAKER_00] Takva je stvar i Europe,

2259
01:15:18,479 --> 01:15:19,899
